 Media Video: What Your Business Actually Needs to Know"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-teal pl-4","children":"Not all social media video is created equal. Here's a practical guide to understanding formats, platforms, and when to hire a professional."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/[0.06] mb-10"}]}],["$","article",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16","children":[[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Social media video has become one of the most effective tools a business can use to reach new customers. But the landscape changes fast, the platforms each have their own requirements, and the gap between video that performs and video that gets ignored is wider than most people think."]}],["$","p","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Here's a practical overview of what your business actually needs to understand about social media video."]}],["$","h2","2",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Platform Matters More Than You Think"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Different platforms favor different types of content, and what works on one often fails on another."]}],["$","p","4",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Instagram Reels and TikTok"}]," favor short-form vertical video — entertaining, fast-paced, and native-feeling. Highly produced content can actually feel out of place here. Authenticity and trends matter."]}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"YouTube"}]," rewards longer, higher-quality content that people search for. If your business can produce genuine value through tutorials, explanations, or behind-the-scenes content, YouTube can drive traffic for years."]}],["$","p","6",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"LinkedIn"}]," works well for professional, informative video content — thought leadership, company culture, and B2B storytelling."]}],["$","p","7",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Facebook"}]," still has a large audience and favors video that keeps people watching, especially in the first few seconds."]}],["$","p","8",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Knowing where your audience actually is will help you decide where to focus your effort and budget."]}],["$","h2","9",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"The First Three Seconds"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["On every platform, you have about three seconds to give someone a reason to keep watching. If your video starts with a logo animation or a slow establishing shot, most people are already gone."]}],["$","p","11",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["The best social media videos start with something that immediately creates curiosity, delivers a surprising statement, or shows something visually compelling. This isn't just a social media trick — it reflects how attention works when people are scrolling."]}],["$","h2","12",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"When to Hire a Professional"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Not every social media video needs a professional crew. Authentic, phone-shot content often performs well — sometimes better than highly polished work. But there are situations where hiring a professional makes sense:"]}],["$","ul","14",{"className":"list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"**Brand launch or major announcement** — First impressions stick"}],["$","li","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"**Product showcase** — Lighting and composition directly impact whether your product looks appealing"}],["$","li","2",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"**Testimonials and interviews** — Audio quality and framing affect credibility"}],["$","li","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"**Ad creative** — Money you're spending on ads is wasted if the video doesn't convert"}],["$","li","4",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"**Anything representing your business at a high-visibility moment**"}]]}],["$","p","15",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["A professional content creator who understands social media platforms is a different skill set from a traditional videographer. When hiring for social media content, look for someone who understands the platforms, not just someone who shoots great video."]}],["$","h2","16",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Consistency Beats Perfection"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["One of the most common mistakes businesses make is producing one or two excellent videos and then going quiet. Consistency — showing up regularly with useful, relevant content — matters more than any single piece of video."]}],["$","p","18",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["If your budget allows for a monthly content session with a social media creator, that's often more valuable than one expensive production every six months."]}],["$","h2","19",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Gulf Coast Businesses Have a Natural Advantage"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["The Gulf Coast is visually compelling. The water, the food, the culture, the outdoor lifestyle — these are assets that translate beautifully to video. Businesses in this region have a natural storytelling advantage that many markets would pay for. Use it."]}]],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal/10 to-transparent border border-teal/20 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest mb-3","children":"Find a Professional on the Gulf Coast"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted text-sm mb-6","children":"Browse verified media professionals available for your next project — from Tallahassee to New Orleans."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/browse","className":"btn-teal font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Browse Pros"}],["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/post-job","className":"btn-outline font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Post a Job"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-navy2 border-t border-white/[0.06] py-12 px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-6xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest mb-8 text-center","children":"More Guides"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5","children":[["$","$L2","how-to-prepare-for-a-professional-video-shoot",{"href":"/blog/how-to-prepare-for-a-professional-video-shoot","className":"card p-5 hover:border-teal/40 transition-all duration-200 group","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-condensed text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase bg-teal/10 text-teal border border-teal/20 px